reviewText: My daughter is totally in love with Nat Wolff and the Naked Brothers band and this series. This was a cute little movie. My daughter and I felt bad for Alex in this movie. My daughter wasn't even upset when Nat and Rosalina kissed again. If your child is into NBB, then of course you will have to buy this movie. If I remember right there are 4 songs from the season 2 cd.
